OL,3,GWales
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FEarly heavy,
OL,6,Fpossible thundery showers will die out
OL,7,Fduring the evening to leave a largely
OL,8,Fdry night. Some clear intervals,
OL,9,Falthough low cloud, and some mist and
OL,10,Ffog patches are likely to form.
OL,11,
OL,12,CWednesday:FEarly low cloud and mist
OL,13,Fwill soon lift to leave a mostly fine
OL,14,Fday across the country. A few showers
OL,15,Fduring the morning with sunny spells
OL,16,Fdeveloping during the afternoon.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
